{"tid":1511484,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"打著紅旗反紅旗唔係指舉支那旗咁撚膚淺","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T20:54:06.000Z","uid":58841,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"745fdb47f2eaf9426e68fc4ae6d4c8fc8322ba23","tid":1511484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:16:44.000Z","msg":"所謂打著紅旗反紅旗<br />\n係指用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅旗既招數</span></span>去打對家<br />\n中共以三大目標三大準則為前提<br />\n拖 壓 氹<br />\n拖=即係將件事不斷拉長 不了了之 例如中美貿易戰支那就不斷拖侵仔<br />\n壓=鎮壓<br />\n氹=即係用懷柔手段令你相信佢<br />\n三大準則 分化 抹黑 滲透<br />\n所以要學識以牙還牙 以眼還眼<br />\n唔係舉五星旗咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘比人以為你係愛國者<br />\n想學人用呢招真係唔該你地去讀熟中共歷史同何為共產主義先黎出聲<br />\n其實中共用既招數真係70年無變過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb3cbfb4d1ce8212da84acb55a388177d04ef58","tid":1511484,"uid":230890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44782631a230c9349570d0e4480d7ac9a7440543","tid":1511484,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"有道理幫推"},{"pid":"3ec54996bdc171c01e7485ad42d1de3e9d7e039e","tid":1511484,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:30:50.000Z","msg":"咪撚再舉支那旗咁on9"},{"pid":"46537255ddf178d76820c5a59fc2a407e3535c50","tid":1511484,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4898082e97c7413a8dc0839daaa125a3f8329fd7","tid":1511484,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"十點一齊嗌：九月一，入機場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYreJMR.gif\" data-thumbna